### Common issues

| Symptom | Likely cause | Fix |
|---------|-------------|-----|
| `Connection refused` on port {{SERVICE_PORT}} | Service not running | `docker compose up {{SERVICE_NAME}} -d` |
| `Queue not found` errors | LocalStack not running or TF not applied | `docker compose up localstack -d && cd terraform && terraform apply` |
| `Import error` | Missing dependency | `pip install -r requirements.txt` |

